{"tid":2028318,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警察濫權及暴力行為登上維基百科首頁","createTime":"2020-05-21T17:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T16:30:30.000Z","uid":71237,"like":127,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"f3e121a1c3bcd391bf49d0582c3d9a4f2841791d","tid":2028318,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:49:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>你知道嗎？</strong><br />\n在反對逃犯條例修訂草案運動中，香港警察對傳媒記者採用了哪些濫權及暴力行為？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/51A2nSi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F51A2nSi.png&h=4d2c5917&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家click入嚟睇下到底有咩濫權及暴力行為啦。<br />\n<a href=\"https://w.wiki/RUT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fw.wiki%2FRUT&d=ppuFFh6piFuOrul45s7BzUqdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=3b260189\" target=\"_blank\">https://w.wiki/RUT</a>"},{"pid":"731e3907a1d2a26d7846a17de2c76444ccc77343","tid":2028318,"uid":71237,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:50:17.000Z","msg":"1.1 向記者開槍射擊<br />\n1.2 向記者投擲或發射催淚彈<br />\n1.3 水炮車攻擊記者<br />\n1.4 盾牌襲擊記者<br />\n1.5 胡椒噴劑攻擊記者<br />\n1.6 使用強力閃光妨礙採訪<br />\n1.7 推跌及打記者<br />\n1.8 使用警棍攻擊記者<br />\n1.9 拘捕採訪的記者<br />\n1.10 蓄意公開記者個人資料<br />\n1.11 喝令記者下跪及濫用暴力<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eUAYFEA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeUAYFEA.png&h=7e5b3202&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6561de753ce0ee95c8fd1354948e1c157316973c","tid":2028318,"uid":92467,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:52:40.000Z","msg":"正，有冇Eng ver"},{"pid":"4c5f7d884950b3ff2c2530a4e7365ccbc0d1d622","tid":2028318,"uid":89184,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:53:28.000Z","msg":"推，最好有埋英文"},{"pid":"5e2628a9c6af0b1dbc19ead2d37ceb2f2085feb3","tid":2028318,"uid":60287,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:54:30.000Z","msg":"wiki中文圈好多五毛<br />\n<br />\nbackup定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e309073115457576cf5cf05cc4af5cee43081042","tid":2028318,"uid":85649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:56:44.000Z","msg":"推到有高手譯英文"},{"pid":"895845a441ad5dd5f0069183df588fbfd4f98c87","tid":2028318,"uid":71237,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"5e2628a9c6af0b1dbc19ead2d37ceb2f2085feb3","tid":2028318,"uid":60287,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:54:30.000Z","msg":"wiki中文圈好多五毛<br />\n<br />\nbackup定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T18:00:32.000Z","msg":"維基百科有「修訂歷史」，就算有人惡意破壞，都有方法可以recover返。<br />\n同埋維基百科有既定嘅規則，就算有大陸人做admin都唔代表可以為所欲為。依一年入面手足已經同五毛、藍絲交手過好多次。"},{"pid":"6e5d40e99d727b496551233d744cb380f49256f9","tid":2028318,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T18:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99344fa04ca8be7da55233d41a21e79c703fd78","tid":2028318,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T18:01:50.000Z","msg":"入去睇下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23145276b2333ace105777af25be21811689f52","tid":2028318,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T18:09:34.000Z","msg":"而家先知原來維基有首頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73e68bccd898aa76f5040f04b6ebe32e4132384","tid":2028318,"uid":71237,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T18:10:07.000Z","msg":"趁機同大家介紹下維基百科的玩法。<br />\n你可以見到入面每一句都有報章做資料來源。原則上你寫每一句都一定要引用資料，咁先唔會俾五毛輕易刪除。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wf4R0La.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWf4R0La.png&h=bf1a6388&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mdjKBiv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmdjKBiv.png&h=eaf291cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以寫維基百科就好似整理報章資料咁，你需要搜集有關「香港警察對傳媒記者的濫權及暴力」的新聞報導，然後經整理後用自己文字再寫出嚟。<br />\n所以寫維基百科唔需要好嘅文筆，只係需要有搜集資料的能力。"},{"pid":"8d282bee8cd722f6b1f72cee2e62f0d4c19fdf39","tid":2028318,"uid":127067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T18:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd59ee037da320f73b16f576fba9d549e2612b8","tid":2028318,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T18:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d9c40d221e17663b38ab10f96aee4bfc961814","tid":2028318,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T18:17:05.000Z","msg":"做好文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082b5c8d50e3e723e44bbe5b42f25f048e63b750","tid":2028318,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T18:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927b002627e866b817ba6caaa0cf896572e3351f","tid":2028318,"uid":87437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T18:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\